Screen 2 Lifx

Match the lighting of your display to your lifx.

Currently only works with hard coded lamp id, and windows games work randomly.

install on windows
------------------

- install python 2.7 (feel free to provide patch for 3.4)
- install python PIL (http://www/pythonware.com/products/pil)
- install numpy ()
- install scipy ()
- install lifx-sdk
